channel.title: 100 errors [F2P Remake Source]
channel.description:
Ok, so for those who don't know my [semi] popular F2P Remake source has 100 errors and I have come to the same error again. I would like to continue my work and release a more updated version of the source though it'd be quite useless with these errors so could somebody tell me how to fix them. Or better yet fix them and re-upload the source?
The source can be found in this thread: [url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,438392.0.html]http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,438392.0.html[/url]
I will Rep if you want it :)
P.S Before anyone says something about Eclipse. I can't download it on the computer I'm coding from :rolleyes:
